data.description: This home is located near Parks, Newer shopping center and restaurants. This is ideal for a big family and if you are looking for bedroom in the main level this home has 2 full bathrooms and 2 bedrooms on it. The kitchen has plenty of cabinets and pantry, it does need some tlc and flooring as there was a leak from washer. The rest of the home has beautiful flooring. upstairs you have a spacious Loft, a hallway that has desk areas, 4 spacious bedrooms. The Yard is a very good size one and with room to have an RV Access Lots of potential.
